we are going to learn LOOPS and WHILE loops in 
loop = loops are used to repeat instructions.
------------------------------------------------------
i = 1
while i <= 5 :
    print("jasveer singh")
    i += 1

print("stop")

output would be 5 times jasveer singh and then stop 
------------------------------------------------------
count till 5 in asending order

i = 1
while i <= 5:
    print(i)
    i += 1

print("loops end")
--------------------------------------------
count from 5 to 1 in desending order

i = 5
while i >= 1 :
    print(i)
    i -= 1
print("loops end")
------------------------------------------------
Q; print 1 to 100 in loops

i = 1

while i <= 100:
    print(i)
    i += 1

print("end")
--------------------------------------------------
Q : print 100 to 1 in loops

i = 100 

while i >= 1:
    print(i)
    i -= 1

print("loop end")
---------------------------------------------
Q: print the multiplicatin of a N number

i = 1

while i <= 10:
    print(5*i)
    i += 1
print("end")
--------------------------------------------------
Q: print the list of number and their square root or under root

part one 
nums = [1, 4, 9, 16, 25, 36, 49, 64, 81, 100]

idx = 1
while idx < len(nums):
    print(nums[idx])
    idx += 1
xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
part two
nums = [1, 4, 9, 16, 25, 36, 49, 64, 81, 100]

idx = 1
while idx < len(nums):
    print(idx)
    idx += 1

